lead_paragraph: Luis Suarez scored two second-half goals to lead Barcelona to a 2-1 comeback victory over 10-man Atletico Madrid in the first leg of their Champions League quarterfinal on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Suarez Nets 2, Barca Comes Back to Beat 10-Man Atletico 2-1
